column5: Got out Saturday for the 1st time and won the Dunnville Hunters & Anglers derby with a 21.50 King and was leading the St Kitts derby for the 1st day ...looks like its going to be a good season for Kings ...my boat will be in Port Weller before May 1st Yahoo bye Kitty Cats got the Salmon Fever now ...
Nice fish dude! Congrats on the derby!
Excellent !  A sweet fish dude.  Now I'll have salmon on the brain until at least September.
Planning on hitting that area in the next few days. Any word on depths the fish have been taken in.? greatly appreciated!
Andy, is longshank part of this board or no?
congrates on the win...  ...curious though ....do you eat the fish out of lake O ?
Yes I do in the Spring ...love them smoked or BBQ ....
